<hgroup><h1>Evaluation of Electronic Health Record Implementation in an Academic Oculoplastics Practice</h1></hgroup><div class="cg p">
<a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Chen%20AJ"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id1"><span class="name western">Allison J Chen</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id1">
